<DOCNO> FBIS3-22438 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "jpten008___94071" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   JPRS-TEN-94-008 </AU>
Document Type:JPRS 
Document Title:Environmental Issues 

<DATE1>  16 March 1994 </DATE1>

