<H3> <TI>   Number of New HIV Cases Climbs to 561 in 1993 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1302173894 Vienna DER STANDARD in German 12 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> AU1302173894 </F>
<F P=104>  Vienna DER STANDARD </F>


