Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Over 150 more Vietnamese have been confirmed 
infected with HIV virus, which can cause AIDS. It raises the 
number of reported cases to 1,167. The new HIV cases include 
the first ever in Lang Son Province, a booming trade center on 
